## Total Cost Breakdown

| Category | Free Tools | Monthly Cost |
|----------|-----------|-----------------|
| AI/LLM | OpenAI Free Tier, Ollama | $0-5 |
| Framework | CrewAI, LangChain, Autogen | $0 |
| Monitoring | Comet, Opik, W&B Free | $0 |
| Database | PostgreSQL, MongoDB Atlas | $0 |
| Hosting | Replit, Railway, Render | $0-5 |
| APIs | n8n, Discord, Telegram | $0 |
| CI/CD | GitHub Actions | $0 |
| **TOTAL** | **ALL ITEMS** | **$0-10/month** |

